
This library was develop quickly as a demonstration of feasibility
 of the cryptosystem presented in the article

FHE Bootstrapping in less than a second, 
by LÃ©o Ducas and Daniele Micciancio, 
avaliable at https://eprint.iacr.org/2014/816.

