Here is a non-exhaustive list of improvement that could be added
- Support for other operation than NAND
- Usage of NTT rather than complex FFT. 
- Vectorialization of linear algebra operations.

Here is a non exhaustive list of NECESSARY modification for any use
 of this library beyond scientific curiosity
- Replace calls to Rand() by cryptographic pseudo-randomness.
